title: Bump csv-parse from 4.4.5 to 4.4.6

labels.name: dependencies
labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

body:
Bumps [csv-parse](https://github.com/wdavidw/node-csv-parse) from 4.4.5 to 4.4.6.
Changelog *Sourced from [csv-parse's changelog](https://github.com/adaltas/node-csv-parse/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md).* > ## Version 4.4.6 > > * security: remove regexp vulnerable to DOS in cast option, npm report 69742
Commits - [`fe3fe58`](https://github.com/adaltas/node-csv-parse/commit/fe3fe58e93f028889e7c0c609c06938073723d1d) Bump to version 4.4.6 - [`b9d3594`](https://github.com/adaltas/node-csv-parse/commit/b9d35940c6815cdf1dfd6b21857a1f6d0fd51e4a) security: remove regexp vulnerable to DOS in cast option, npm report 69742 - See full diff in [compare view](https://github.com/wdavidw/node-csv-parse/compare/v4.4.5...v4.4.6)

[![Dependabot compatibility score](https://dependabot-badges.githubapp.com/badges/compatibility_score?dependency-name=csv-parse&package-manager=npm_and_yarn&previous-version=4.4.5&new-version=4.4.6)](https://help.github.com/articles/configuring-automated-security-fixes) Dependabot will resolve any conflicts with this PR as long as you don't alter it yourself.
